This map consist of 12 musics, all fit nicely into the gameplay. All song credits goes to their rightful newgrounds.com authors.

4 Ramps will toggle every minute, opening and closing, so you get two different experiences with and without the ramp.

Buytime has been setup to 5 minutes as default time per round.

Airaccelerate has been changed to 500 in order to have the maximum fun. On top of this, sv_enablebunnyhopping, sv_enableboost has been set to true.

Bombsite has been added so map resets when the time runs out when there are enough players. However, C4 cannot be planted at the bombsite.

Question/Comments/Bug? Leave them here!
Please Rate and explain, thank you very much!

This is a very simple, yet stategic team deathmatch map. The entire map is divided into 4 colours: red, orange, blue and green, and it is completely symetric so no team has an advantage over the other. In order to win you must know the map well and use the given teleports wisely. There are in all 6 teleports. There are two on the bridges and 4 on the edges of the tower. To use the ones on the bridges, you will have to press E while standing and aiming at the "Lambda"-logo (HL-logo).
Note that bots tend to like sniping a whole lot in this map, so keep that in mind.
I made this as a "gift" to the website: www.pixel.tv, which is a Danish gaming website and also is the reason for the pixel.tv logo in the skybox and the big "Pixel"-sign.
I hope you enjoy this map!
Enjoy!
